The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Punters Corner - Belmont Stakes
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           Belmont Stakes 
                          
	Elmont (New York): Big Browns Triple Crown dreams wilted on Saturday when 38-1 longshot Da Tara won the Belmont Stakes in a wire-to-wire shocker. Bidding to become the first Triple Crown winner since Affirmed in 1978, Big Brown sat in third for most of the race but had nothing down the stretch and finished last. (Reuters)                                                                                                                                                                       
